mapper.select: select p.seller_id, u.nickname, avg(r.star_point) as avg_star_point, u.profile_image from product p left join user u on u.user_id = p.seller_id left join review r on p.product_id = r.product_id group by u.user_id,p.seller_id order by avg_star_point desc limit 5;
SELECT * FROM user where email = #{email} and password = #{password};

select * from user u left join f_info f on user_id=f_id left join review r on seller_id = user_id where u.type=2 and u.user_id=#{seller_id} group by user_id,f.address2,f.address,f.introduction,f.switchAt,r.review_id;
SELECT name FROM user where email = #{email}
SELECT name FROM user where nickname = #{nickname}
